Factors in childhood associated with lung function decline to adolescence in 
cystic fibrosis.

Begum N(1), Byrnes CA(2), Cheney J(3), Cooper PJ(4), Fantino E(1), Gailer N(3), 
Grimwood K(5), GutierrezCardenas D(1), Massie J(6), Robertson CF(6), Sly PD(7), 
Tiddens HA(8), Wainwright CE(9), Ware RS(10).
